  "model_notes": "Position 1: E = 3-door Hatchback, F = 5-door Hatchback. Position 2: AE = CG10DE engine, AN = CG13DE engine. Position 3: A = 2-wheel drive. Position 4: R = Right-hand drive, L = Left-hand drive. Position 5: B = L grade, D = LX grade, F = SLX grade, T = SUPER S grade. Position 6: F = 5-speed manual transaxle, Z = N-CVT. Fixed segment: K11. Suffix 1: E = E.G.I. Suffix 2: E = For R.H.D. markets, F = For South Europe, G = For Central Europe, S = For North Europe. Suffix 3: A = Standard equipment."
